0c4d63c2-4d64-4bc7-b1c7-a938d4641776.title: Khazard Warlord
0c4d63c2-4d64-4bc7-b1c7-a938d4641776.text:
Don't speak to me you insignificant wretch! Die in the
name of Khazard!

b8348c8c-1375-4346-b936-2d886a237e8a.title: Note
b8348c8c-1375-4346-b936-2d886a237e8a.text: cant get the orbs til king bolren asks you to find the warlord

1af519e5-6639-4316-bfa3-e9e5ff48e2bb.title: Khazard warlord
1af519e5-6639-4316-bfa3-e9e5ff48e2bb.text: Go back to your pesky little green friends.

8bc1b6b1-9c91-409d-8b73-eff5fce84cd1.title: Khazard warlord
8bc1b6b1-9c91-409d-8b73-eff5fce84cd1.text:
You're out of your depth traveller. These orbs are part
of a much larger picture.

119ce456-12a9-4a70-8a05-09da424e6d5e.title: <player>
119ce456-12a9-4a70-8a05-09da424e6d5e.text: They're stolen goods, now give them here!

12452561-e4b0-47d5-8adc-3179935948c4.title: Khazard warlord
12452561-e4b0-47d5-8adc-3179935948c4.text:
Ha, you really think you stand a chance? I'll crush
you.

770645d7-ce5b-4080-8b6a-4d689343c0b6.text:
As the warlord falls to the ground, a ghostly vapour
floats upwards from his battle-worn armour. Out of
sight you hear a shrill scream in the still air. You spot
the orbs of protection among his remains.

085e3c53-6bf6-495b-b7c1-743b4d6e9f79.title: Note
085e3c53-6bf6-495b-b7c1-743b4d6e9f79.text:
when warlord dies and
drops orbs of protection

453d1dd0-98c9-4701-9b47-ca48b83e913f.title: Khazard warlord
453d1dd0-98c9-4701-9b47-ca48b83e913f.text:
Fool, warriors blessed by Khazard don't die. You can't
kill that which is already dead. However I can kill you!
